    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/4d5c84c078d83f70d40d3ae339d95b88.poster.avif?t=1771270940\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/4d5c84c078d83f70d40d3ae339d95b88.webm?t=1771270940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/4d5c84c078d83f70d40d3ae339d95b88.mp4?t=1771270940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>Solar Wave</strong>》是一款超大规模的太空战略游戏，采用间接控制机制，经济、战争与扩张在整个星系中展开。<br>第二十一千年。人类的太阳帝国已经征服银河系，并将目光投向邻近的星系。新的世界早已有人居住，但这无法阻止人类无情的扩张。你将扮演帝国总督，决定殖民地的命运，指挥庞大的舰队，并左右横跨宇宙的战争走向。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>真正的大规模战略</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在银河尺度上做出决策。探索恒星系统，扩张帝国疆域，占领战略要地，并规划长期发展。《<strong>Solar Wave</strong>》将经典 4X 的核心理念与一个不断变化、充满生命力的宇宙相结合。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>间接控制与自主舰队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里没有繁琐的微观管理。你设定的是目标，而非单艘飞船的具体指令。舰队会自主行动，根据局势变化做出反应，将指挥转化为真正的战略思考，而不是机械式操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/c8595d00267d14a05bd5d874f3ec2b51.poster.avif?t=1771270940\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/c8595d00267d14a05bd5d874f3ec2b51.webm?t=1771270940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/c8595d00267d14a05bd5d874f3ec2b51.mp4?t=1771270940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>经济即力量</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个深度互联的经济系统是帝国的核心。殖民地开采资源、建立生产链，并为战争机器提供补给。强大的后勤与工业体系，才是每一支胜利舰队背后真正的武器。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>银河规模的战争</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>Solar Wave</strong>》的太空战斗宏大而残酷。数千艘战舰在壮观的战场上交锋，胜负取决于事前的准备，而非操作速度。真正的胜利，在第一炮打响之前就已注定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/e56bf5a81c21f1426d9f72bb20f782bc.poster.avif?t=1771270940\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/e56bf5a81c21f1426d9f72bb20f782bc.webm?t=1771270940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212820/extras/e56bf5a81c21f1426d9f72bb20f782bc.mp4?t=1771270940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采用间接控制的大战略玩法，无需繁琐的微观管理</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直接影响战争与扩张的动态经济系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与数千艘战舰的史诗级太空战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满黑暗太空歌剧氛围的震撼视觉效果</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人难忘的沉浸式配乐</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入人类横跨群星的无情进军，在《<strong>Solar Wave</strong>》中体验第二十一千年的冷酷未来。</p>",
